### Server-Side Data Fetching with useDataTable Hook in React

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/features/data-table/GUIDE.md

Illustrates how to utilize the useDataTable hook to fetch server-side data, including limit, offset, and sorting parameters, for API calls. This pattern is essential for efficient data management in server-side operations.

```tsx
// Get current table state for API calls
const { limit, offset, sorting } = useDataTable();
const columnFilters = useColumnFilters();

// Use in your API call
const { data } = trpc.users.list.useQuery({
  limit,
  offset,
  sorting,
  filters: columnFilters,
});
```

