### Get Booking Transcripts (API)

Source: https://context7.com/calcom/cal.com/llms.txt

Retrieves Cal Video transcripts for a given booking. The API requires the booking UID and authentication. Transcripts are provided with download links that are valid for a limited time (1 hour). The response includes the transcript ID and its expiration time.

```bash
# Get transcripts for a booking
curl -X GET https://api.cal.com/v2/bookings/bk_abc123xyz/transcripts \
  -H "cal-api-version: 2024-08-13" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer cal_live_***"
```

